Package: pseudobulkDGE
Type: Package
Title: Pseudobulk Differential Gene Expression for Single-Cell / Single-Nucleus RNA-seq
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Castaldi", email = "peter4244@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Reusable pipeline for cell-type pseudobulk differential gene
    expression on multi-subject single-cell or single-nucleus RNA-seq data.
    Accepts either a Seurat object or a directory of per-sample 10x mtx
    triplets (with cell_metadata.tsv carrying sample_id and cell-type
    annotation), aggregates to per-(sample x cell-type) pseudobulk, and
    runs both limma/voom (with optional voomWithQualityWeights and
    candidate-gene force-retention) and dreamlet (precision-weighted
    pseudobulk) differential expression. Includes parameterized Rmd
    templates that produce HTML reports following lab conventions.
